reviewText: OMG IS SO FUNNY I LOVE THAT THANKS FOR GREAT PRICE AND FAST DELIVERY
I am very pleased with this product. It is exactly what i choose to buy...!!! Good product and i would buy another one.
I've never laughed so hard. Showed it to my native speaking students and a lot of the jokes went right over their head. Oh well! I loved it.
Good classic movie; thought it'd be in color but overall a good film. The movie wasn't for me but I believe the recepient enjoyed it.
Great movie, great actor and I love the way he dances...Highly recommend this film to all races that love the Latino Flavo.

We are a bilingual family,my kids speak both English and Spanish perfectly. This was the kind of movies I saw as a child and we wanted to share with our kids one of the greatest  Latin comics. They learned to love Cantinflas and The Three Stooges. Now my kids are grown men but they still love those old movies they saw with us. This one is one of the funniest by this great artist. The movie is very hard to find it was great to find it at Amazon.
With Cantinflas you can never go wrong. Hilarious comedy.
It's an excellent order; it's very good picture; it has very good sound.  I have saw it two times and I am very satisfied with it.
